Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要按照练习来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不想有那样的经历了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞  最后一击！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐好像精神点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  七海  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…就想问问看新作怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感觉心动不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「恋爱真好啊」这样的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  仁写的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为是动作类的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了七海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份剧本能借我用一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话我想在试镜的时候用用看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2月14号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那不是情人节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个课题中有一环是自由发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请务必借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  七海愿意演的话  我也会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就尽情用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是努力的女孩子们的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我也要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2月14号吗…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么一大早情绪就这么高涨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哥哥你太消沉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2月13日是水高的入学考试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前一天我会去你那住的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好坦诚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥难得这么坦诚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算拒绝了  你也会自说自话过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挂咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥还是一如既往的冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是很重要的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是计划书的发表会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发表会那是什么  好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你还真信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是像考试一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  哥哥也要考试了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子把精神分给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君  你脸色不太好  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发表会是今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯  放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  我一定会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这么冷的天你一个人在那热血什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去澳大利亚玩得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这种事  神田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在发表之前就已经变得这么僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  别想着要做地怎么怎么完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？但是这种时候果然还是应该要努力拼一下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是笨啊  我就是叫你不要拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迎来了新的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长的话还真是长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  是学弟君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嘞  是仁学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我模仿牛蛙的叫声可不会输给任何人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这种自信给我丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  学姐你是想和仁学长说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁学长  你不打算回樱花庄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在考试之前我都会寄宿在前学生会长家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我可没听你提过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说了  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关照你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  久等了  总一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皓皓眼里只有总一郎君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然啦  他是我的恋人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也想谈一场你们这样的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  不能打扰情侣们毕业前的宝贵时光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…仁学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你帮我和美咲说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是没事的话就把这只牛蛙给我带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过前学生会长竟然能听出是牛蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学弟君  我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以学弟君也要加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把气势  紧张与不安全部发泄出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能会给你造成压力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是想说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用短信还是能说出口的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神田空太  请多指…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤泽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次看到有人真的会把头撞在麦克风上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是看到了珍贵的画面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是叫你不要拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  就为大家介绍「节奏战士」的企划内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,类别是节奏动作战斗游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配合乐曲的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好时机按下按键进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以一首歌曲结束之前打倒对手为目标的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来为大家说明一下实际的操作方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影像和乐曲共同演绎的是这个企划的特点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次播放已经完成了曲目时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就相当于完成了一个非常华丽的影像片段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤泽如果你那边来做这个游戏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多少开发资金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想  算上测试费要一亿日币吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花一千万做试玩版
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式版需要七千万吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过给谁做  都会觉得很头疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一张2200日币的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最少就要卖45000张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标销售量就要达到10万张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  我想为大家总结一下本企划的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配合乐曲  华丽地击倒敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是本企划的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断给玩家带来爽快感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并通过网络分享这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并目标成为「玩着开心  看着也开心」的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是本企划的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  神田空太先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾的是  我们的结论是本公司很难接手您的企划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果您同意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以允许我们的工作人员来改善您的计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是一半合格了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家之后先发邮件给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们这边做好准备之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再商定下次讨论的日程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.16,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(395,123)\frz5\fs20}发表会非常成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.16,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(401,180)\frz5\fs20}这都多亏了大家的帮忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.16,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(279,231)\frz5\fs20}谢谢大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得问了也是白问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是要问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是红豆饭配牛脏锅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便提一下  牛脏锅可是博多特产
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强调博多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是白问了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我给大家盛饭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在房间里吃牛脏锅太那啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君真的恭喜你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大家给我庆祝我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  企划案真的要通过还要一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不算是合格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那通过了之后  要办个更盛大的庆祝宴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人连发表会都参加不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  青山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没给你添麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我很有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在发表会之前青山发了加油的短信给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么要让我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.87,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(312,193)\frz7\fs23}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说短信会让你有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要说的话至少说句恭喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那和七海的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是不一样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差别对待？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太对七海一个人很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都在对椎名特别照顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  也谢谢椎名你帮我画的企划书的画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了那张画  说明起来轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就轮到青山了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试镜加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么时候来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然说有事要和我说  是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还是蛮重要的事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事一直想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜…喜…喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得我都害羞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是演戏演戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那从头再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然说有事要和我说  是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还是蛮重要的事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着神田君和青山就觉得心里毛毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛毛的是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里感觉有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是最重要的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你看这个学习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有把这份毛毛的感觉发泄到漫画里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发泄到漫画里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海这可是好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的茧  你老爱说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为剧本里写了喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就趁练习直接告白得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田也接受了的话 说明他也是有点在意你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要情人节了  不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行  说到底这只是为了试镜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能带着这么不纯的动机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是纠结的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去告白吧告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然说有事要和我说  是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还是蛮重要的事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事一直想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就趁练习直接告白得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（感谢光临）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白也在加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  游戏的理念就按照这个来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  发表会上的那张插画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁画的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那是樱花庄…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是同一个宿舍的人画的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在樱花庄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是千寻老师的学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您认识千寻老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我们是同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画那幅画的是老师的表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那难道喵波隆的画也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  请她帮忙画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤泽先生来看喵波隆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这部游戏里也请保持那份热情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个月的菜花庄好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  真白姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我的建议起作用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待见到本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲姐的常夜锅  多谢款待啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把我的头脑奉献给水高的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水高要是变成优子这种水平的话会让人很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好过分啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  真白姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个月也好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节将近  男生女生的那种坐立不安的感觉真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白姐还真是只要努力做了就一定能做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你用的是长者的口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天终于就要到情人节了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心都在那上面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般会更关心明天的考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  虽然的确如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节是女孩子们能拿出勇气的特别的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  美咲姐说得太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}美咲姐果然是优子的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}亲手做的吗  能送出去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子酱  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  你洗好的衣服一直就这么晾在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经帮你叠好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用麻烦你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你今天也会很晚回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:18:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭菜要帮你加热吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴室也空着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  我先吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥和七海姐到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么哥哥那么照顾七海姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被空太照顾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白姐是没救了的孩子  不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事一直想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然需要警惕的不是真白姐而是七海姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同居第二年的男女关系真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那个真实的数字到底是哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真白姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不像样的打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}哥哥快逃  会被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}为什么不穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为空太不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我现在在帮优子铺床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太是能干的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少不会穿越和分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是典型的地球人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太  你要看到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这幅难为情的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H  色狼  不知廉耻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有自觉的话就不要穿成这样出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在妹妹面前失去理性的话怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是禽兽  禽兽哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么说话方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在动摇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在吹头发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  明明在那卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是什么值得大惊小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这种在伤口上撒盐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越过了大人的阶梯好担心明天的考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心  优子是只要努力做的话就一定能做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长者的口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦  优子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然提前了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然让妈妈帮了忙  是今年我做的手工巧克力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试结束之后就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以先给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子是不会输给你们俩位的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是情人节了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白姐和七海姐哪个是你的真命天女
